Package: niche
Title: Entry Point for the Niche R Universe for Consumer Psychology Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Josh", "Gonzales",
           email = "jgonza10@uoguelph.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides a minimal, stable user interface for the niche R universe,
    which supports reproducible, audit-ready consumer psychology research. This
    package delegates specification parsing to 'vision' and structural contracts
    to 'nicheCore', serving as the primary entry point for defining, building,
    and executing research workflows.
